WEBVTT

00:14:58.546 --> 00:15:01.752
one is an African American male,
John Rogers, who founded the firm,

00:15:01.776 --> 00:15:02.936
and one is a white male.

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:06.357
I would argue that when you look
at investment firms around the nation,

00:15:06.381 --> 00:15:08.658
I'd love to see that level of diversity,

00:15:08.682 --> 00:15:11.625
where women actually
have the majority in that situation.

00:15:11.649 --> 00:15:15.331
CA: And despite a significant blip
during the financial crisis,

00:15:15.355 --> 00:15:19.307
I mean, by many measures,
Ariel has performed incredibly well.

00:15:19.331 --> 00:15:20.490
MH: We believe so.

00:15:20.514 --> 00:15:24.268
I mean, certainly the financial crisis
was a come-to-Jesus moment for our firm,

00:15:24.292 --> 00:15:26.659
2008 was the worst year
in the history of Ariel.

00:15:26.683 --> 00:15:29.736
But since that time,
our recovery has been spectacular.

00:15:29.760 --> 00:15:31.958
We're in the top of our peer group.